raspimidihub (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * First stable release
  * Automatic all-to-all MIDI routing with hotplug support
  * Per-connection MIDI channel and message type filtering
  * MIDI mapping engine (Note→CC, Note→CC toggle, CC→CC, Channel remap)
  * MIDI Learn for auto-detecting source events
  * Mobile-first web UI with connection matrix, presets, MIDI monitor
  * Built-in WiFi access point with captive portal
  * WiFi client mode with network scanner and auto-fallback to AP
  * Configuration persistence with stable USB device identification
  * Piano keyboard and CC slider for MIDI test sending
  * LED status indication (green ACT blinks on MIDI, red PWR off = healthy)
  * Reboot from web UI
  * mDNS hostname: raspimidihub.local

 -- Daniel Kraft <wam@poplr.de>  Sat, 05 Apr 2026 21:00:00 +0200
